QuestData.Title: Lil' Tika
QuestData.Description: <The tiny armored raptor scratches pitifully at the cage's wooden bars. As you approach, the miniscule reptile wiggles frantically and issues a piercing screech for help!$b$bPerhaps you can open the cage and let it free.>
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Deliver Lil' Tika to Beastmother Jabati.
